title: 이달의소녀탐구 #339 (LOONA TV #339)
members: Olivia Hye, Go Won, Chuu, Yves
summary:
0:05 -- Go Won and Yves wave hi to the camera while posing.
0:11 -- Hye mentions that they are on a bus to the airplane.
0:16 -- Yves and Chuu play the 3 syllable game. Yves gives Chuu "프" (p-eu) as the
first syllable. Chuu replies with 프라이 (fry). Then she gives her 하 (ha) and Chuu replies
with "하쉬영" (Ha Soo-young) which is Yves' real name.
0:24 -- It has been a while since Yves has heard that and is about to tear up
0:40 -- yyxy selca.
0:45 -- Chuu: "Take a picture of me~!"
0:56 -- They finally arrive in Budapest and there are some fans waiting for them
